<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>To whom it may concern,<br>
<br>
I will not pretend to be something different than what I am, so for this cause, I shall tell you out front; I am a quiet man, and a bit of a lone wolf, as you might say. I travel with my companion, a young arctic wolf, Snow Shadow, in search of knowledge and the power to defeat my enemies. <br>
<br>
I wish a brethren, but one that thusly respects the fact that after spending many a night alone upon the tundra of Everfrost, I am quite accustomed to being on my own, and as such, being regarded as cold. See me as you will. This is not a call to acclaim my glories or my faults, merely a request to any fellowships that seek a competent beastlord in their ranks.<br>
<br>
Regards,<br>
Mondego</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <br>
